{"type":"answer","id":109149,"parentType":"question","parentId":13573,"uid":15246,"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/IIBp49c.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IIBp49c.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/IIBp49c.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>樓主太懶了<br>\n爐子火不夠大都能成為理由，與其坐在那裡抱怨難道不會主動去想辦法改變嗎？<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/EmcxRXe.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EmcxRXe.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/EmcxRXe.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/LmQKZN7.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LmQKZN7.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/LmQKZN7.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>不是加拿大不好，而是樓主的懶給自己生活無形中增添了很多障礙；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/rrHwWnN.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rrHwWnN.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/rrHwWnN.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>家裡父母太寵了吧？習慣了被伺候、被指揮、衣來身手飯來張口；<br>\n樓主應該改變國內養成的被動的習慣；<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/eDu0F7N.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eDu0F7N.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/eDu0F7N.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Osl05OJ.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Osl05OJ.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Osl05OJ.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>加拿大不是大麻合法嗎？抽抽大麻，混混大蔴圈，交交朋友，不要把自己框得死死的：“這個是毒品，我不碰；那個又是XXX外國人才做的，<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/SNykvrb.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SNykvrb.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/SNykvrb.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>我做不來”<br>\n如電影《肖申克的救贖》述，在體制內生活慣了，被“institutionalized”了<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5AV5Xz1.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5AV5Xz1.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/5AV5Xz1.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>，尿尿都要獄警批准<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Th1Mp31.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Th1Mp31.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Th1Mp31.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>；<br>\n樓主要反思是否被共產黨塑造的生活、思想囚禁<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHuqhFU.gif \" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHuqhFU.gif \" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHuqhFU.gif \" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gnoamzv.gif \" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gnoamzv.gif \" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gnoamzv.gif \" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>“移民加拿大” 和 “讓你快樂” 不是因果關係，如果要說什麼東西一定”讓你快樂“，那麼只有一個答案：海洛因<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NVmcfxg.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NVmcfxg.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NVmcfxg.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/CvCT6Hj.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CvCT6Hj.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/CvCT6Hj.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>“快樂”是一個非常自我的概念；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/BRLpBYR.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BRLpBYR.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/BRLpBYR.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>“快樂”必須是自己爭取，有幸得到，也只有自己享用<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-20","agreeCount":126,"discussionCount":17}